Description_lang: Rejuvenation healing is increased by up to $s1%, and Tranquility healing is increased by up to $s2%, healing for more on low-health targets.

description_blz.en_US: Rejuvenation healing is increased by up to 10%, and Tranquility healing is increased by up to 20%, healing for more on low-health targets.
description_blz.es_MX: La sanación de Rejuvenecimiento aumenta hasta un 10%, y la de Tranquilidad hasta un 20%. Sanan más cantidad de salud a objetivos con menos salud.
description_blz.pt_BR: A cura de Rejuvenescer é aumentada em até 10% e a cura de Tranquilidade é aumentada em até 20%, curando mais em alvos com pouca vida.
description_blz.de_DE: Erhöht die Heilung von 'Verjüngung' um bis zu 10% und die von 'Gelassenheit' um bis zu 20%. Ziele mit niedriger Gesundheit erhalten mehr Heilung.
description_blz.en_GB: Rejuvenation healing is increased by up to 10%, and Tranquility healing is increased by up to 20%, healing for more on low-health targets.
description_blz.es_ES: La sanación de Rejuvenecimiento aumenta hasta el 10% y la sanación de Tranquilidad aumenta hasta el 20%. La sanación aumentará más sobre objetivos con poca salud.
description_blz.fr_FR: Augmente les soins de Récupération d’un maximum de 10% et ceux de Tranquillité d’un maximum de 20%. Les cibles ayant moins de points de vie sont soignées davantage.
description_blz.it_IT: Aumenta le cure fornite da Rinvigorimento fino a un massimo del 10% e le cure fornite da Tranquillità fino a un massimo del 20%, in base alla salute mancante ai bersagli.
description_blz.ru_RU: Сила исцеления "Омоложения" увеличивается максимум на 10%, а "Спокойствия" – максимум на 20%. Цели с низким уровнем здоровья получают больше исцеления.
description_blz.ko_KR: 회복의 치유량이 최대 10%만큼, 평온의 치유량이 최대 20%만큼 증가합니다. 대상의 생명력이 낮을수록 치유량이 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 回春術的治療效果最多提高10%，寧靜的治療效果最多提高20%，對於生命力越低的目標，治療效果提高越多。
description_blz.zh_CN: 对低生命值目标的治疗效果提高，回春术最多提高10%，宁静最多提高20%。
